    InodeFile, InodeFolder

    public abstract class Inode
extends ImageWriter
implements Comparable<Inode>
    Inode is an abstract class, with information shared by all types of Inodes.

      • Inode

        protected Inode(String name,
     int id,
     int parentId,
     boolean isFolder,
     long creationTimeMs)
        Create an inode.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the inode.
        id - the id of the inode, which is globally unique.
        parentId - the id of the parent inode. -1 if there is no parent.
        isFolder - if the inode presents a folder
        creationTimeMs - the creation time of the inode, in milliseconds.
